message:
President Recep Tayyip Erdoğan & I interacted with business leaders & addressed a business summit in Delhi.

India & Turkey share good economic ties but there is immense scope to further deepen our business relations for the benefit of our people. Tie-ups through more trade, FDI & in areas such as technology, MSMEs, energy can give a strong impetus to bilateral relations. http://nm-4.com/4ws4
